        {
            "title": "美銀下調印度經濟成長預測,警告通膨風險上升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/urfrUn3tlZ3lRbIjaJ3zKg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/India_flag_M_1440056035.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 美國銀行已下調其對印度的經濟成長預測並上調通膨預期,警告稱中東衝突導致的能源價格長期衝擊已開始對該國經濟造成明顯影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美銀經濟學家Rahul Bajoria將該行對2027財年GDP成長預測從7%下調至6.5%,同時將通膨預測從4.7%上調至5.2%,原因是將原油價格基準從先前假設的每桶77.50美元上調至92.50美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行警告稱存在進一步的下行風險,指出\"如果衝突加劇或拖延,我們的成長預測面臨1-2個百分點的下行風險\"。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-86f0dbf4-2383-31bb-ab6c-7f913cb425e7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據稱,3月份的早期高頻數據顯示出新興壓力。製造業PMI跌至2022年6月以來的最低水平,成本通膨創43個月新高。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著航空燃油價格上漲,3月份國際航空客運量年減18%,而汽車銷售和信貸成長則持續保持穩定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美銀指出貿易條件惡化是關鍵傳導管道,預計較高的能源成本將在一至三個月內傳導至批發價格。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在貨幣政策方面,美銀現在預期印度儲備銀行將轉向更為鷹派的立場。Bajoria寫道:\"根據我們目前的成長-通膨動態,我們預計印度儲備銀行將在2027財年加息50個點子\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E9%8A%80%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC-%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-151730573.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 23:57:32",
