        {
            "title": "川普發出伊朗衝突升級信號,多倫多證交所料低開",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4_XxvWezeu3t0ocUageFGw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/Toronto Stock Exchange_800x533_L_1449415495.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 加拿大主要股指週四料將大幅低開,因中東衝突可能持續的擔憂重燃,令全球市場陷入恐慌。截至<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"美國東部時間\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:美國東部時間;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/美國東部時間\">美國東部時間</a>08:10,S&amp;P/TSX 60期貨下跌25.6點,跌幅1.34%,逆轉了前一交易日因停火希望而帶來的漲幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">S&amp;P/TSX綜合指數週三上漲0.58%,當時市場樂觀預期敵對行動即將結束。然而,在美國總統川普於白宮發表講話,誓言加強對德黑蘭的軍事行動後,市場情緒在隔夜轉為悲觀。</p><h3 class=\"mb-module-gap text-px20 font-bold lg:text-px18 text-batcave\"><strong>美股回落</strong></h3><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">華爾街期貨顯示開盤前將出現大幅拋售。截至美國東部時間8:15,道指期貨下跌670點,跌幅1.43%,標普500指數期貨下跌1.65%,納斯達克100指數期貨下滑2.07%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7682985d-5b81-3dbe-8901-635a53031d9f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次回落是在川普週三晚間發表講話之後,他表示軍方將在未來兩到三週內加強行動。他重申華盛頓不會主導重新開放霍爾木茲海峽的努力,敦促依賴石油的國家自行確保通道安全。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><h3 class=\"mb-module-gap text-px20 font-bold lg:text-px18 text-batcave\"><strong>油價飆升</strong></h3><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週四油價大漲,因軍事升級的可能性威脅到進一步的供應中斷。布蘭特原油期貨攀升至每桶109.07美元,而WTI原油期貨飆升10.06%,突破110美元大關。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價飆升反映出市場對霍爾木茲海峽的日益擔憂,這條重要水道承載著全球20%的石油消費,目前實際上仍處於封鎖狀態。川普警告稱,如果無法達成協議,美國將\"同時\"且\"極其猛烈地\"打擊伊朗的電力基礎設施。</p><h3 class=\"mb-module-gap text-px20 font-bold lg:text-px18 text-batcave\"><strong>黃金連漲勢頭中斷</strong></h3><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週四黃金價格結束了連續四天的漲勢,投資者開始適應不斷變化的地緣政治格局。XAU/USD下跌3.11%至每盎司4,612.27美元,從盤中高點4,800.58美元回落。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這種避險金屬的下跌伴隨著大宗商品市場的廣泛波動。白銀期貨暴跌6.99%至每盎司70.79美元,鉑金期貨下跌3.45%至1,922美元,市場正為美國軍事行動加劇的影響做好準備。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E7%99%BC%E5%87%BA%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A%E4%BF%A1%E8%99%9F-%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%AB%E5%A4%9A%E8%AD%89%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80%E6%96%99%E4%BD%8E%E9%96%8B-133411962.html",
